  "detailed_description": "Help Kate Robinson, an amateur travel blogger, and her daughter Nicole save a picturesque hotel on their first to Paris in this hidden-object adventure, <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >First Time in Paris!</h2> Revitalize the Hôtel Hospitalité and find yourself in the lively Parisian environment as you discover the hidden treasures and picturesque streets of the city.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1767150/extras/3054d2eec492935afe79780bd16326ad.poster.avif?t=1729486956\" width=600 height=372 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1767150/extras/3054d2eec492935afe79780bd16326ad.webm?t=1729486956\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1767150/extras/3054d2eec492935afe79780bd16326ad.mp4?t=1729486956\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Experience the true essence of the City of Love by mingling with French locals and embracing the city's unique culture. With over 30 unique minigames, including solving mysteries at cozy cafés and finding treasures in bustling marchés, there's always a new Parisian adventure waiting for you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1767150/extras/1e784e7b4d91a191214315bdaa62ff27.poster.avif?t=1729486956\" width=600 height=372 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1767150/extras/1e784e7b4d91a191214315bdaa62ff27.webm?t=1729486956\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1767150/extras/1e784e7b4d91a191214315bdaa62ff27.mp4?t=1729486956\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore stunning Parisian scenes<br></li><li>Help Kate rescue the Hôtel Hospitalité<br></li><li>Enjoy over 30 engaging minigames inspired by Paris<br></li><li>Revisit locations in Unlimited Mode<br></li><li>Unlock achievements as you play<br></li><li>Download exclusive wallpapers and the full soundtrack</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1767150/extras/c218da3455df0dcb11aa2c5fd59f5f7e.poster.avif?t=1729486956\" width=600 height=372 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1767150/extras/c218da3455df0dcb11aa2c5fd59f5f7e.webm?t=1729486956\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1767150/extras/c218da3455df0dcb11aa2c5fd59f5f7e.mp4?t=1729486956\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Join Kate and Nicole and discover the heart and soul of Paris! <br>Bienvenue à la Ville de l'Amour!",
  "about_the_game": "Help Kate Robinson, an amateur travel blogger, and her daughter Nicole save a picturesque hotel on their first to Paris in this hidden-object adventure, <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >First Time in Paris!</h2> Revitalize the Hôtel Hospitalité and find yourself in the lively Parisian environment as you discover the hidden treasures and picturesque streets of the city.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1767150/extras/3054d2eec492935afe79780bd16326ad.poster.avif?t=1729486956\" width=600 height=372 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1767150/extras/3054d2eec492935afe79780bd16326ad.webm?t=1729486956\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1767150/extras/3054d2eec492935afe79780bd16326ad.mp4?t=1729486956\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Experience the true essence of the City of Love by mingling with French locals and embracing the city's unique culture. With over 30 unique minigames, including solving mysteries at cozy cafés and finding treasures in bustling marchés, there's always a new Parisian adventure waiting for you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1767150/extras/1e784e7b4d91a191214315bdaa62ff27.poster.avif?t=1729486956\" width=600 height=372 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1767150/extras/1e784e7b4d91a191214315bdaa62ff27.webm?t=1729486956\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1767150/extras/1e784e7b4d91a191214315bdaa62ff27.mp4?t=1729486956\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore stunning Parisian scenes<br></li><li>Help Kate rescue the Hôtel Hospitalité<br></li><li>Enjoy over 30 engaging minigames inspired by Paris<br></li><li>Revisit locations in Unlimited Mode<br></li><li>Unlock achievements as you play<br></li><li>Download exclusive wallpapers and the full soundtrack</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1767150/extras/c218da3455df0dcb11aa2c5fd59f5f7e.poster.avif?t=1729486956\" width=600 height=372 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1767150/extras/c218da3455df0dcb11aa2c5fd59f5f7e.webm?t=1729486956\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1767150/extras/c218da3455df0dcb11aa2c5fd59f5f7e.mp4?t=1729486956\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Join Kate and Nicole and discover the heart and soul of Paris! <br>Bienvenue à la Ville de l'Amour!",
